COMMERCIAL ENTERPRISE ADDENDUM:

For the purposes of this license, a "Commercial Enterprise" is defined as any
entity that meets ONE OR MORE of the following criteria:

1. Has annual revenue exceeding $10 million USD (or equivalent in other currencies)
2. Has more than 500 employees
3. Is publicly traded on any stock exchange
4. Is a subsidiary of, or is controlled by, an entity meeting any of the above criteria

COMMERCIAL ENTERPRISE LICENSE REQUIREMENT:

If you are a Commercial Enterprise as defined above, you must obtain a separate
commercial license from the copyright holder before using this Software in any
capacity. This includes but is not limited to:

- Using the Software in production environments
- Distributing the Software as part of your products or services
- Modifying the Software for internal use
- Using the Software for evaluation or testing purposes

